   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">There are multiple different measurements that can be viewed in
the display, and some can be accessed in multiple ways.<note class="- topic/note ">The screenshots
are only samples. The available measurements depends on configurations,
settings and system state.</note>
         <ul class="- topic/ul ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">System Measured Values</uicontrol>: Quick access to main measurements about the output.</p>
            </li>
            <li platform="Modular-DC Modular-AC" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Unit State (Rectifier Modules)</uicontrol>: Detailed measurements
about the rectifier modules.</p>
            </li>
            <li platform="Modular-Inverter Modular-AC" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Unit State (Inverter Modules)</uicontrol>: Detailed measurements
about the inverter modules.</p>
            </li>
            <li platform="Modular-Inverter Modular-AC" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Unit State (SBS Modules)</uicontrol>: Detailed measurements about
the static switch module and the manual bypass module.</p>
            </li>
            <li platform="Modular-DC Modular-AC" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Unit State (Batteries)</uicontrol>: Detailed measurements about the
batteries.</p>
            </li>
            <li platform="Modular-DCDC-Converter" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Unit State (Converter Modules)</uicontrol>: Detailed measurements
about the converter modules.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">
                  <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Measured Values (Protocol)</uicontrol>: Detailed configured list of measurements about the system, modules
and batteries.</p>
            </li>
         </ul>
      </p>
      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">System Measured Values</title>
         <sectiondiv class="- topic/sectiondiv ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">To view
the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">System measured values</uicontrol> click
on <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Measurement icon</uicontrol> in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Status
bar</uicontrol> at the bottom of the screen.</p>
            <fig platform="Modular-DC" class="- topic/fig ">
